      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_c041b873e994" name="type" type="_enum_91d752053b2c"/>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_83cb188efd77" name="evidence">
        <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#String"/>
      </ownedAttribute>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_ref_42d897f8d64a" name="jurisdiction" isOrdered="false" type="_cls_b9e788a49d4a">
        <upperValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralUnlimitedNatural" xmi:id="_uv_9334ef131bce" value=""/>
        <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_cmt_33001d394467">
          <body>Replaces the former free-text 'jurisdiction' string. References the canonical Jurisdiction instances in RegulatoryContext, preventing synonymous strings (EU / European Union / Europe) for the same jurisdiction and enabling cross-law queries.</body>
        </ownedComment>
      </ownedAttribute>
    </packagedElement>
  </packagedElement>
  <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Package" xmi:id="_pkg_7c04d34498ca" name="Processing">
    <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Class" xmi:id="_cls_8a62db5f5283" name="ProcessingActivity">
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_b6b01c0cfa1e" name="activityId">
        <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#String"/>
      </ownedAttribute>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_9137679eb405" name="description">
        <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#String"/>
      </ownedAttribute>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_8394023b02b5" name="action" type="_enum_53dd59329b7f"/>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_prop_9d65696d4a31" name="riskAssessmentReference">
        <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_lv_0382726910d5" value="0"/>
        <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#String"/>
        <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_cmt_49b17a84b0d5">
          <body>Law-neutral reference to any form of impact or risk assessment document (DPIA under GDPR Art.35, RIPD under LGPD Art.38, risk assessment under CPRA, voluntary PIA under PIPEDA). Absence on high-risk activities is a compliance gap signal, not a hard conformance error.</body>
        </ownedComment>
      </ownedAttribute>
      <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_ref_f7bf52699e29" name="dataProcessed" isOrdered="false" type="_cls_6041fb5e6dad">
        <upperValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralUnlimitedNatural" xmi:id="_uv_2b4fe1b9c8c9" value=""/>
        <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_cmt_a855f348e768">
          <body>One activity to many data categories; one data category to many activities.</body>
        </ownedComment>
      </ownedAttribute>
      <ownedRule xmi:type="uml:Constraint" xmi:id="_con_24fb3d5becaf" name="constraint_3__warning" constrainedElement="_cls_8a62db5f5283">
        <specification xmi:type="uml:OpaqueExpression" xmi:id="_oex_d615703e0c7b">
          <language>OCL</language>
          <body>(self.action = ProcessingAction::Transfer or self.action = ProcessingAction::Share) and self.dataProcessed-&gt;exists(d | d.sensitivity = SensitivityLevel::SpecialCategory or d.sensitivity = SensitivityLevel::High) implies self.riskAssessmentReference-&gt;notEmpty()</body>
        </specification>
        <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_cmt_dba490c4472f">
          <body>High-risk Transfer or Share of sensitive data has no risk assessment reference. This is a hard violation under GDPR Art.35 and LGPD Art.38, a regulatory obligation under CPRA, and a best-practice recommendation under PIPEDA.</body>
        </ownedComment>
      </ownedRule>
    </packagedElement>
  </packagedElement>
